TWO young men were lucky to escape with their lives on
Friday when they were bust stealing pork.According to The
Monitor, Patrick Magada (20) and Isaac Mutebe had visited the Nabirumba
Road Pork joint in Kamuli, north of Kampala in Uganda.They then ordered a kilogram of fried pork. While they
